<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101015509693183></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101015509693183><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=13&mid=101015509693183>RE: Charm questions</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=13&mid=101015509693183#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=125338><span id= >srik</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jan 4th 9:38 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>I have read a lot of discussion regarding the effect of charisma on charm, mez, etc...  Many people argue that CHA is worthless, max out int.  I can only assume that they are lower level.  It most certainly has a noticable effect on charms and (more importantly) mezes.  However, unlike other posts, based on a limited observation, I refer you to the following:<br><br>Caster's Realm Nes Archive, November 10, 1999<br><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/archives.asp?Day=All&amp;Month=11&amp;Year=1999&amp;Action=View" target=_new>http://eq.castersrealm.com/archives.asp?Day=All&amp;Month=11&amp;Year=1999&amp;Action=View</a><br><br>October 8, 1999<br><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/archives.asp?Day=All&amp;Month=11&amp;Year=1999&amp;Action=View" target=_new>http://eq.castersrealm.com/archives.asp?Day=All&amp;Month=11&amp;Year=1999&amp;Action=View</a><br><br>Charisma affects the resist rate for all charm and mez-type spells (not just enchanters), and DOES affect the duration of charm.  Charisma does not affect buffs.<br><br>I hope this helps.<br><br>-Srik<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
