	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here is a fun and effective strategy a friend taught me.  Get in a group with another chanter, 3 wizzies (mages can work too) and a cleric. i did this in lguk, just a good place for this strategy. heres what you do: fear one mob, let it go and find some friends. will pull back a ton of mobs if lucky, keep mezzin the ones that come till you are sure that all are there. then someone gives a cue, in my case it was &quot;FIRE&quot; and the two chanters start chain casting the 2 stun spells, while the nukers chain cast their aoe dds and cleric group heals when needed if anyone gets bashed on. so we died a few times... but its fun imo, and you can actually rake in a lotta exp if you do it right! i have heard of people takin out near 50 mobs at once doin this, i dont know that first hand though =) <br><br>Aeterna Sedai<br>38 Chanter on Povar<br>Kindred Honour<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec  4 03:31:04 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
