	   <tr><td colspan=2>Good ol'MI.<br>This does work. Remember, most people (and creatures) do not see behind their heads. Long distance a &quot;friendship&quot; spell to one of the guards outside, invis. Walk up behind the merchant you'd like to speak with; be out of line of sight to others, MI. Do your business, invis, drop MI and waltz out.<br>(oh, and beware that frigg'n Brownie Scout that roams - even when I went back that way at 46 he's a PITA)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Dec 23 01:45:09 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
